Patrol Lookout Climber Kids Outdoor Playtime Fun With CKN
snippet.description:
Hi guys, today i'm putting together this Paw Patrol Lookout Climber by Step 2. This is a real life size version of the Paw Patrol Lookout Tower.
“No job's too big, no pup's too small - Paw Patrol, we're on a roll!” 
Transport your little rescuers to the thrills of Adventure Bay with this outdoor kid’s climber that will keep them occupied for hours! Little Marshalls, Rubbles and Chases can climb up the ladder to the lookout tower, spot their friends in need through the lookout periscope and then slide to the rescue.

snippet.title: Kids Ride On Bike Park Playtime Fun CKN
snippet.description:
Hi guys, today we are Unboxing this new Power Wheels Paw Patrol 12V Electric Battery-powered ride on car.We are so excited to put this one together because it looks just like Ryder's Quad bike  in Paw Patrol.
Cool PAW Patrol graphics, flashy-looking wheels & accents and realistic Kawasaki KFX styling team up to take you on imaginative, off-road ATV rescue adventures!The Monster Traction system on this battery-powered ride-on powers through rough terrain, including ruts, wet grass, gravel, mud, and more, while the twist-grip throttle revs it into high speed! Kids will feel like, "No job is too big, no pup is too small" when they're riding to the rescue on this Power Wheels  PAW Patrol Kawasaki KFX!
Hope you guys enjoy this video and please don't forget to subscribe to CKN
